WEBVTT

00:00:01.127 --> 00:00:03.293
Most of you will know

00:00:03.317 --> 00:00:07.888
about the challenges faced
by my beloved continent, Africa.

00:00:08.635 --> 00:00:10.809
Too many people are poor.

00:00:11.149 --> 00:00:14.061
Millions of girls
don't have access to school.

00:00:14.085 --> 00:00:18.299
And there aren't enough jobs
for the rapidly growing population.

00:00:19.434 --> 00:00:20.671
Every day,

00:00:20.695 --> 00:00:25.395
33,000 new young people
join the search for employment.

00:00:25.419 --> 00:00:29.076
That's 12 million
for three million formal jobs.

00:00:29.482 --> 00:00:30.958
In sub-Saharan Africa,